title: Episode 291: Throat Olympics (Feat. BRS Kash)
itunes:title: Episode 291: Throat Olympics (Feat. BRS Kash)
description:
Rapper BRS Kash,is here to promote his latest album “Kash Only.” Kash breaks down the absolutely CRAZY story as to how the song “Throat Baby” came to life, his go to dishes in the kitchen that helps seal him the deal, as well as a detailed step by step process in regards to giving good oral. BRS Kash and Gigi may even have made a little love connection…enjoy!
